OL,3,CNetanyahu to 'increase the blows' as
OL,4,CIsraeli military strikes Hezbollah
OL,5,Csites
OL,7,FIsrael's military says its air force
OL,8,Fstruck sites belonging to Hezbollah in
OL,9,FLebanon.
OL,11,FThe strikes in Bekaa Valley on Monday
OL,12,Fnight came as Israeli Prime Minister
OL,13,FBenjamin Netanyahu vowed to intensify
OL,14,Fattacks in the latest Israel-Hezbollah
OL,15,Fwar.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
