OL,3,CNetanyahu to 'increase the blows' as
OL,4,CIsraeli military strikes Hezbollah
OL,5,Csites
OL,7,FNetanyahu's warning came as Hezbollah
OL,8,Fhas been firing fiber optic drones, a
OL,9,Fweapon used widely in the war in
OL,10,FUkraine, at Israeli forces in southern
OL,11,FLebanon and northern Israel in recent
OL,12,Fweeks.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
