OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1779747066
OL,3,CNetanyahu to 'increase the blows' as
OL,4,CIsraeli military strikes Hezbollah
OL,5,Csites
OL,7,F"We will hit them. It's true that they
OL,8,Fare shooting drones at us, fiber optic
OL,9,Fdrones. We have a special team working
OL,10,Fon that and we will solve that too,"
OL,11,FNetanyahu said in a video posted on
OL,12,Fsocial media. "What this requires of
OL,13,Fus now is to increase the blows, to
OL,14,Fincrease the intensity. We will smite
OL,15,Fthem hip and thigh."
OL,17,FDespite a US-brokered ceasefire since
OL,18,FApril, tensions remain high.
