OL,5,Csites
OL,7,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,8,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,9,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,10,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,12,FA US State Department official said
OL,13,FHezbollah has ignored requests to stop
OL,14,Ffiring.
OL,16,FMonday's escalation comes as Lebanese
OL,17,Fand Israeli officials are set to meet
OL,18,Fon Friday at the Pentagon to discuss
OL,19,Fthe ceasefire.
