OL,3,CNetanyahu to 'increase the blows' as
OL,4,CIsraeli military strikes Hezbollah
OL,5,Csites
OL,7,FThe latest Israel-Hezbollah war began
OL,8,Fon March 2, when Hezbollah fired
OL,9,Frockets into northern Israel, two days
OL,10,Fafter the US and Israel began their
OL,11,Fattacks on Iran.
OL,13,FMore than 3,000 people have been
OL,14,Fkilled in Lebanon in the latest
OL,15,Ffighting, according to the Lebanese
OL,16,FHealth Ministry.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/6
