OL,3,CNetanyahu to 'increase the blows' as
OL,4,CIsraeli military strikes Hezbollah
OL,5,Csites
OL,7,FAlso, 22 Israeli soldiers and a
OL,8,Fdefence contractor have been killed in
OL,9,For near southern Lebanon, and two
OL,10,Fcivilians have been killed in northern
OL,11,FIsrael, according to Netanyahu's
OL,12,Foffice.
